= Huanle Xu -- Background and CV

 	
My name is Huanle Xu. I received my BSc(Eng) degree from the Department of Information Engineering, Shanghai Jiao Tong University (SJTU) in 2012 and my Ph.D. degree from the Department of Information Engineering, The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK) in 2016. My PhD supervisor is [http://staff.ie.cuhk.edu.hk/~wclau Wing Cheong Lau] who is the director of [http://mobitec.ie.cuhk.edu.hk Mobitec Center] in CUHK. I am particularly interested in designing wonderful algorithms for real applications and practical systems using mathematical tools.

